theorem
Th35: ( sgn ( x * y ) ) = ( ( sgn x ) * ( sgn y ) )
proof
A1: ((( 0 ) < x & ( 0 ) < y) implies ( sgn ( x * y ) ) = ( ( sgn x ) * ( sgn y ) ))
proof
assume that
A2: ( 0 ) < x
and
A3: ( 0 ) < y;
A4: ( sgn y ) = 1 by A3,CKB15:def 1;
(( ( 0 ) * y ) < ( x * y ) & ( sgn x ) = 1) by A2,A3,CKB15:def 1,XREAL_1:68;
hence thesis by A4,CKB15:def 1;
end;
A5: ((( 0 ) < x & y < ( 0 )) implies ( sgn ( x * y ) ) = ( ( sgn x ) * ( sgn y ) ))
proof
assume that
A6: ( 0 ) < x
and
A7: y < ( 0 );
( sgn y ) = ( - 1 ) by A7,CKB15:def 1;
then A8: ( ( sgn x ) * ( sgn y ) ) = ( 1 * ( - 1 ) ) by A6,CKB15:def 1
.= ( - 1 );
( x * y ) < ( ( 0 ) * y ) by A6,A7,XREAL_1:69;
hence thesis by A8,CKB15:def 1;
end;
A9: ((x < ( 0 ) & y < ( 0 )) implies ( sgn ( x * y ) ) = ( ( sgn x ) * ( sgn y ) ))
proof
assume that
A10: x < ( 0 )
and
A11: y < ( 0 );
( sgn y ) = ( - 1 ) by A11,CKB15:def 1;
then A12: ( ( sgn x ) * ( sgn y ) ) = ( ( - 1 ) * ( - 1 ) ) by A10,CKB15:def 1
.= 1;
( x * ( 0 ) ) < ( x * y ) by A10,A11,XREAL_1:69;
hence thesis by A12,CKB15:def 1;
end;
A13: ((x < ( 0 ) & ( 0 ) < y) implies ( sgn ( x * y ) ) = ( ( sgn x ) * ( sgn y ) ))
proof
assume that
A14: x < ( 0 )
and
A15: ( 0 ) < y;
( sgn y ) = 1 by A15,CKB15:def 1;
then A16: ( ( sgn x ) * ( sgn y ) ) = ( - 1 ) by A14,CKB15:def 1;
( x * y ) < ( ( 0 ) * y ) by A14,A15,XREAL_1:68;
hence thesis by A16,CKB15:def 1;
end;
((x = ( 0 ) or y = ( 0 )) implies ( sgn ( x * y ) ) = ( ( sgn x ) * ( sgn y ) ))
proof
assume A17: (x = ( 0 ) or y = ( 0 ));
then (( sgn x ) = ( 0 ) or ( sgn y ) = ( 0 )) by CKB15:def 1;
hence thesis by A17;
end;
hence thesis by A1,A5,A13,A9;
end;
